title: Dmitri Zornikov
text:
Dmitri Sergeyevich Zornikov (; born 28 April 1997) is a Russian <a href="association%20football">football</a> player.
Club career.
He made his debut in the <a href="Russian%20Professional%20Football%20League">Russian Professional Football League</a> for <a href="FC%20Khimki">FC Khimki</a> on 23 May 2016 in a game against <a href="FC%20Spartak%20Kostroma">FC Spartak Kostroma</a>. He made his <a href="Russian%20Football%20National%20League">Russian Football National League</a> debut for Khimki on 12 November 2017 in a game against <a href="PFC%20Krylia%20Sovetov%20Samara">PFC Krylia Sovetov Samara</a>.
